cast.overview: Cold War spy Greville Wynne and his Russian source try to put an end to the Cuban Missile Crisis.
cast.title: The Courier

cast.overview: Caleb, a coder at the world's largest internet company, wins a competition to spend a week at a private mountain retreat belonging to Nathan, the reclusive CEO of the company. But when Caleb arrives at the remote location he finds that he will have to participate in a strange and fascinating experiment in which he must interact with the world's first true artificial intelligence, housed in the body of a beautiful robot girl.
cast.title: Ex Machina

details.biography: Elina Alminas was born in Tallinn, Estonia. She moved to UK to pursue her acting career and has a degree in Theatre and Performance from Goldsmiths, University of London. Since graduation Elina has been working on stage and screen in both comedy and drama. She is fluent in English, Estonian and Russian.
details.name: Elina Alminas
